1
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:00,000
The Story of Ming Lan

2
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,580
Episode 56

3
00:01:05,240 --> 00:01:06,440
Slow down. Slow down.

4
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:08,880
Move.

5
00:01:09,880 --> 00:01:10,920
Left. Left.

6
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:14,440
We're not going to Jiaxi House. Go to my study.

7
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:15,680
Marquis,

8
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:17,760
why go to the study?

9
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:19,120
Go to the study!

10
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:21,400
Marquis, you got injured so badly.

11
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,680
If you don't let Big Madam see it,

12
00:01:23,080 --> 00:01:23,880
won't you

13
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:24,320
have suffered in vain?

14
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:25,880
Let her see?

15
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:27,280
For what then?

16
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,080
I won't let her see it!

17
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:29,560
Go to the study.

18
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:32,509
Study. Study.

19
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:33,560
Slowly.

20
00:01:36,051 --> 00:01:37,691
Slow down! Slow down!

21
00:01:46,252 --> 00:01:47,492
Did you hear it clearly?

22
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:48,560
Quite clearly.

23
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,440
Shitou said that Marquis was beaten

24
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:51,750
to a bloody pulp.

25
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,360
The wound in his chest has just healed.

26
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:58,480
How could he get injured again?

27
00:02:01,821 --> 00:02:02,861
Big Madam.

28
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:22,720
Who is it?

29
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:26,800
It's me. It's me.

30
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:28,880
So, you're here.

31
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:35,840
How come the doctor isn't here yet?

32
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:40,320
Even for all the doctors in this world,

33
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:43,400
they are no match for my adhesive surgical plaster.

34
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:45,320
Just then,

35
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:46,400
Shitou has dressed the wound.

36
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:53,760
Marquis,

37
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:56,240
just stay at home and rest for the next few days.

38
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,450
Recuperate from the wound

39
00:02:57,450 --> 00:02:58,640
and skip the court then.

40
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:13,400
Wife, I'm in so much pain.

41
00:03:14,690 --> 00:03:15,040
Then...

42
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:18,000
I'll use the fan to make you feel cooler.

43
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,400
You'll not be that painful then.

44
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,120
Wife,

45
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:36,560
I really feel better now.

46
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:42,040
But the part with no wound is also cold.

47
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:46,200
Then I'll get some ice.

48
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:48,400
It's okay. I'm fine now.

49
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:50,280
It won't hurt anymore with some ice.

50
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,560
Why are you getting ice?!

51
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:53,400
Wife, don't get them anymore.

52
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:55,120
Ice can stop the pain.

53
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:57,960
I can't really apply it for the whole day, right?

54
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,880
It will still ache later,

55
00:03:59,881 --> 00:04:00,600
right?

56
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:06,200
Why must you do this?

57
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,200
Look at this, this injury of mine,

58
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,680
it wasn't in vain.

59
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:14,040
I'll go to the ice cellar and get you some ice.

60
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,280
Wife!

61
00:04:16,520 --> 00:04:17,480
Oh, Wife...

62
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:23,000
Just lie down properly!

63
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,320
Shitou!

64
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:27,400
Go.

65
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,240
Go and get me some ice from the ice cellar.

66
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,160
Okay.

67
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:34,120
Quickly just lie down properly.

68
00:04:44,570 --> 00:04:46,280
Wife, don't worry.

69
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:48,360
I'm not worried.

70
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,160
These matters

71
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,960
are just political conflicts.

72
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,880
I just unitedly stood

73
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:57,920
on the side of His Majesty.

74
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,800
It looks kind of scary,

75
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:00,920
but it's really nothing.

76
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:02,560
My joints and bones aren't harmed.

77
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,880
It will be fine in a few days.

78
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:09,640
Your eyes...

79
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:13,040
why do your eyes look red?

80
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,400
They're fine.

81
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:16,640
Just like those of rabbits.

82
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,280
Nonsenseï¼

83
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:32,880
Empress Dowager.

84
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,640
All of you, leave now.

85
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:43,920
Say it.

86
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:46,920
Eunuch Li went out the palace for purchase.

87
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,160
Third Young Master of Gu

88
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,280
just followed him.

89
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:53,360
I got it.

90
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,600
Noble Consort Liu is currently

91
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,800
accompanying His Majesty

92
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,160
in a stroll around the garden.

93
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,720
There's no need to worry

94
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:07,960
about Eunuch Li.

95
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:10,200
You should think about that

96
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,624
what Noble Consort Liu

97
00:06:12,624 --> 00:06:14,400
would be talking with His Majesty now.

98
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,720
You are indeed the Emperor,

99
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:20,240
but also my husband,

100
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:22,080
and that of the Empress.

101
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:24,280
You are also the father of your children,

102
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:26,360
and the son of your father.

103
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:29,240
Before you became the Emperor,

104
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,300
I had been living

105
00:06:30,300 --> 00:06:31,280
in a simple house and ugly alleys then.

106
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,960
But I've never heard that

107
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,800
anyone would meddle in

108
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:35,925
the private affairs

109
00:06:35,925 --> 00:06:37,000
of other families.

110
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:44,320
You think that

111
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:47,760
I should call him Royal Father?

112
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:50,960
As for the address,

113
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,160
Your Majesty,

114
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,960
it's all your own private matter.

115
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,400
Only you

116
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:02,840
can comfort me.

117
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,500
Emperor Dowager,

118
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:12,600
Prime Minister Han is seeking for an audience.

119
00:07:13,520 --> 00:07:15,520
He still dared to see me?

120
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:16,680
Tell him to leave!

121
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,040
Yes.

122
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,680
Wait.

123
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,880
Hey, come here.

124
00:07:42,760 --> 00:07:45,360
Just tell him to wait outside,

125
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:48,080
for I'm ill from severe anger.

126
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:51,680
and unable to get up.

127
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:54,240
Empress Dowager was so mad that she can't breathe,

128
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,680
and is currently resting.

129
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,560
If you have

130
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,680
any other things to do,

131
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:00,440
you'd better attend to them first.

132
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:02,800
If Empress Dowager is sick,

133
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,400
I won't disturb her.

134
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,640
May she just give her approval

135
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:07,720
and write a decree.

136
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:10,840
I will then leave.

137
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:15,760
Lord,

138
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:17,600
we've completed the purchases.

139
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,760
We can go back anytime.

140
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,280
Okay.

141
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:22,960
You all take a rest outside.

142
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,520
We'll leave once everyone's full.

143
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:25,520
Yes.

144
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,280
Official Li!

145
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:33,175
Looking from the outside,

146
00:08:33,175 --> 00:08:34,480
it just looks like you.

147
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,600
It's indeed you then.

148
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,760
Official Gu,

149
00:08:39,800 --> 00:08:41,225
I just came out for purchasing,

150
00:08:41,225 --> 00:08:42,320
and I'm about to leave.

151
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,480
I don't even have any official job.

152
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,960
How could it be official?

153
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:49,040
It's hard to bump into each other out here.

154
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:50,760
Why don't we have a few drinks before you leave?

155
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:53,080
There are urgent matters in the palace.

156
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:55,120
Please forgive me.

157
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,040
Official! Official!

158
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,960
Today, my older brother

159
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,560
got reprimanded in court.

160
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:03,000
Was His Majesty offended?

161
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,650
Marquis Gu

162
00:09:13,650 --> 00:09:15,400
has always been deeply favored by His Majesty.

163
00:09:16,060 --> 00:09:17,800
Even if he does any improper acts,

164
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:20,360
His Majesty won't be mad.

165
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,200
Okay. That's good.

166
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:24,080
It's just that...

167
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,000
It's just that?

168
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,680
It's also natural

169
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:32,120
for Empress Dowager to be mad sometimes.

170
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:35,520
But Empress Dowager is the lord,

171
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:37,360
and Marquis is just a courtier.

172
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:40,040
I'm sure that Marquis

173
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:40,750
won't bear any grudge

174
00:09:40,750 --> 00:09:41,760
against Empress Dowager, right?

175
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:43,440
Official, we won't definitely!

176
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,400
You've said it too seriously.

177
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,200
I just fear of Empress Dowager's discomfort,

178
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:48,360
which makes the whole marquis manor uneasy.

179
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:50,040
We only wish to loyally serve

180
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:52,080
and unburden the worries of Empress Dowager.

181
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:54,600
It's fine. It's fine.

182
00:09:55,160 --> 00:09:56,040
Third, take care!

183
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,360
I'll take my leave then.

184
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,360
Official, let me walk you out.

185
00:09:59,920 --> 00:10:02,040
Based on what Eunuch Li said,

186
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,840
it doesn't seem to be a big problem.

187
00:10:04,734 --> 00:10:07,254
Among his words, "it's just that"

188
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:09,120
bears a greater meaning.

189
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:12,480
Or else, how come you say one thing,

190
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:14,000
and he just have to say another?

191
00:10:14,780 --> 00:10:16,925
Empress Dowager and His Majesty are not united.

192
00:10:16,925 --> 00:10:18,800
Everyone knows that.

193
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:21,200
Even Second Brother got caned by Empress Dowager.

194
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:23,600
So Empress Dowager is bearing grudges.

195
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:24,920
Isn't it quite clear?

196
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:26,840
If it's very clear,

197
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:28,040
why bother saying it?

198
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:34,080
I'm thinking...he just want to swindle us?

199
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:35,800
It's quite easy for him to get money.

200
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,720
Why must he use a few words to swindle you?

201
00:10:38,680 --> 00:10:39,560
Go. Go. Go.

202
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,320
Go back to the library and study more.

203
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:47,440
What does this get to do with studying?

204
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:54,520
What do you think?

205
00:10:54,640 --> 00:10:57,120
When Young Master asked about the Emperor,

206
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:58,550
Officer Li could have just

207
00:10:58,550 --> 00:10:59,560
answered about the Emperor.

208
00:11:00,280 --> 00:11:02,360
How come he mentioned the Empress Dowager then?

209
00:11:03,640 --> 00:11:04,880
He mentioned Empress Dowager

210
00:11:04,880 --> 00:11:06,160
to scare Third Young Master firstly,

211
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:08,300
but then said that everything's fine

212
00:11:08,300 --> 00:11:09,160
and there's still a chance.

213
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:12,400
Previously, it was Eunuch Zhu.

214
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:14,160
Now, it's Eunuch Li.

215
00:11:14,566 --> 00:11:16,600
One works for the Empress Dowager,

216
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:18,360
while the other for His Majesty.

217
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:20,400
But what they said were completely the same.

218
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:24,040
It then means that they are linked together.

219
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:27,240
Even you could notice the intention

220
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:28,560
of Eunuch Li

221
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:30,360
in seeking Tingwei expressively,

222
00:11:32,680 --> 00:11:35,160
but he just couldn't see it.

223
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:38,360
We must act faster.

224
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,600
There's no more time.

225
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,800
Or else, we will die from this slow cooking.

226
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:47,440
That stupid son of mine

227
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:50,360
would also get manipulated.

228
00:11:54,560 --> 00:11:56,440
They are being so unruly.

229
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:58,200
I'll drive them away now.

230
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:02,320
Prime Minister Han

231
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,800
will not go back willingly

232
00:12:05,640 --> 00:12:07,280
without my written decree.

233
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:09,320
Since they all want it,

234
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:12,160
then I'll write His Majesty a decree

235
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:14,280
or favoring his birth family.

236
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:17,560
Not only can he acknowledge him as father,

237
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:20,200
but also as an emperor.

238
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:25,475
Confer his birth mother and illegitimate mothers

239
00:12:25,475 --> 00:12:26,400
as empresses.

240
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,950
Empress Dowager, are you really

241
00:12:27,950 --> 00:12:29,320
backing down to His Majesty?

242
00:12:31,160 --> 00:12:32,000
Let's end it.

243
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,840
Inform the Imperial Kitchen

244
00:12:35,640 --> 00:12:37,280
that the Prime Minister is here.

245
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:39,600
I'll treat him with good dishes.

246
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,560
This was what His Majesty wants.

247
00:13:23,920 --> 00:13:24,800
But as the Empress Dowager

248
00:13:24,800 --> 00:13:25,720
was going to have you beaten,

249
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:27,240
why didn't he stand out and stop it?

250
00:13:28,920 --> 00:13:29,760
Well, now,

251
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,240
you can't even eat properly.

252
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:39,400
Since it was His Majesty's intention,

253
00:13:40,040 --> 00:13:41,480
why would he stop it?

254
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:46,000
Now that you're broken and had to stay at home,

255
00:13:46,880 --> 00:13:48,880
he would have lost help in the imperial court.

256
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:55,120
Except me in the morning court,

257
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:00,360
there are still Xiao Geng

258
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,560
and State Uncle.

259
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:06,800
Previously, when Prime Minister Han

260
00:14:06,800 --> 00:14:08,050
mentioned this matter of addressing

261
00:14:08,050 --> 00:14:09,280
Prince Shu as Royal Father,

262
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:12,200
His Majesty pressed it down.

263
00:14:17,040 --> 00:14:19,200
Now things have become like this

264
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,280
because that His Majesty and Empress Dowager,

265
00:14:21,640 --> 00:14:23,280
they both can't endure it any longer.

266
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:30,000
Couldn't you just keep silent on this?

267
00:14:36,800 --> 00:14:37,920
I...

268
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:41,120
have inherited this marquis title.

269
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:44,200
With His Majesty's writing,

270
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:46,800
I traveled from Yuzhou

271
00:14:46,800 --> 00:14:48,000
to rescue the Late Emperor.

272
00:14:49,160 --> 00:14:51,000
Who would believe that I'm impartial?

273
00:14:52,400 --> 00:14:53,720
Even if I keep silent,

274
00:14:54,280 --> 00:14:55,560
His Majesty and Empress Dowager

275
00:14:55,560 --> 00:14:57,880
would naturally help me choose my side.

276
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:04,800
But being adopted means that

277
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:07,000
you're using other people's surname,

278
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,800
inheriting other people's assets,

279
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:10,240
eating other people's food,

280
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:11,320
and enjoying other people's blessings.

281
00:15:11,920 --> 00:15:13,400
If one day, you become powerful

282
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,960
and you abandon the surname of the adopter

283
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:16,475
and revert it back.

284
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,240
For doing this,

285
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:20,640
a commoner would surely get looked down.

286
00:15:20,800 --> 00:15:22,200
